/// Handle to a config-driven serial device for Rhai scripts
///
/// Wraps GenericSerialDriver from daq-hardware, providing:
/// - Trait-based methods (Movable, Readable, etc.)
/// - Raw transaction API for advanced use
/// - Config and parameter access
